The focus of The Captain Class is team sports. In particular, this thoughtfully-researched book explores the factors that create and perpetuate elite teams that exhibited multiple years of years of superior performance and championship success.

 


[book:The Captain Class: The Hidden Force that Creates the World's Greatest Teams|31869155] is one of the <a href="https://beantownweb.blogspot.com/2018/01/best-business-books-2017.html" target="_blank">Best Business Books of 2017</a>.


